adviseScripts.text: You know what, Commander?

adviseScripts.text: Hm?

adviseScripts.text: Thanks for the idea! Hee hee!

adviseScripts.text: But, I'm supposed to be the big sister!

adviseScripts.text: Take a guess!

Your mindset.
